Detail: DAP with the power of Zinc
Dose: Godavari Ultra DAP is highly suitable for cereals like paddy, wheat and maize. Highly suitable for Zinc deficient soils. Suitable for basal application for almost all crops because Zinc helps good growth in early stages.
Features:
Godavari Ultra DAP is a fortified Di Ammonium Phosphate produced by Coromandel.
Godavari Ultra DAP is fortified with Zinc which is the most vital micro nutrient in Indian condition.
Godavari Ultra DAP provides 18% Nitrogen & 46% Phosphate along with 0.5% Zinc.

Detail: This ideal fertiliser for basal application has Nitrogen at 18% and Phosphorus at 46% and is ideal for crops like paddy, jowar, maize, oilseed crops etc.
Features:
